  <h2 id="Master" class="left">Master Sword<h2>
    <p>
    The master Sword is the hero's main weapon. You normally begin your story getting a simple wood or metal sword and eventually obtain the master sword which is needed to defeat the evil monsters in the world.
    </p>
    
    <h2 id="Rupees" class="right">Rupees<h2>
    <p>
    Rupees are the currency of the world. The basic ones (most of them anyway) appear in every game while the special ones only appear in a few.
    </p>
    <table width="200" border="1">
  <tr>
    <th colspan="3" scope="col">Basic</th>
